# The consumer-bootstrap template bundle MUST ship in the VSIX — the shared
# template writer (gitScaffold / sessionGenPrompt) loads it at runtime from
# dist/templates/. Covered by `!dist/**` above; kept explicit so a future
# .vscodeignore edit cannot silently drop it. Verified with `vsce ls`.
